snippet.title: Space for Sale | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Have you always wanted your own solar system? 

In Space for Sale, now you can live that dream. As a small astronaut, you buy your own solar system and build homes for your alien clients on exotic planets. Explore different worlds, gather resources, and tame flora and fauna on various procedurally generated planets.  

Too scared to go alone? You can team up with a friend to build and explore in co-op mode. 

Space for Sale is coming to PC soon™. 
 
- Links & Info - 
Steam: https://thqn.net/sfs-steam
Website: https://spaceforsale.thqnordic.com
